OL,3,CRunning champion raises over #46,000
OL,4,Cfollowing his death
OL,6,FA fundraiser that was set up by a
OL,7,Fchampion Scottish ultramarathon runner
OL,8,Ffrom Dumfries who died running the
OL,9,FCape Wrath Trail has raised more than
OL,10,F#46,000 pounds.
OL,12,FDavid Parrish was attempting to set
OL,13,Fthe record for the 230-mile unmarked
OL,14,Ftrail from Fort William to Cape Wrath.
OL,15,FIt is a route he had already completed
OL,16,Fwhen he won the Cape Wrath Ultra race
OL,17,Fin 2023.
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G1/7
OL,2,W/.!+.!/*%/.!+,*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
