FL,360,350,120,260,000,100
PN,35902
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F359A1777129865
OL,3,CRunning champion raises over #46,000
OL,4,Cfollowing his death
OL,6,FHe was running the route unsupported
OL,7,Fand raising funds for the Scottish
OL,8,FMountain Rescue team, in memory of his
OL,9,Ffriend, Luke Ireland.
OL,11,FBut he tragically died in similar
OL,12,Fcircumstances.
OL,14,FIn November 2014 David's friend Luke
OL,15,Fpassed away from hypothermia when the
OL,16,Fweather changed as he was running in
OL,17,Fthe mountains around Glen Clova.
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G2/7
OL,2,W/.!+.!/*%/.!+,*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BBorder NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,360,350,120,260,000,100
PN,35903
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F359A1777129865
OL,3,CRunning champion raises over #46,000
OL,4,Cfollowing his death
OL,6,FOn his fundraising page, Parrish
OL,7,Fexplained the events that followed. It
OL,8,Fsaid: "Alongside fellow Marines,
OL,9,Fvolunteers from the Scottish Mountain
OL,10,FRescue deployed in large numbers to
OL,11,Fsearch tirelessly for Luke and,
OL,12,Ftragically, bring him off the hill."
OL,14,FThe runner wanted to support the
OL,15,Fcharity that worked so hard to find
OL,16,Fhis friend on one of hundreds of
OL,17,Fcallouts that year, adding: "The
OL,18,FScottish Mountain Rescue is an
OL,19,Finstitution very close to the hearts
OL,20,Fof many in the outdoors/hiking/hill
OL,21,Frunning community.
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G3/7
OL,2,W/.!+.!/*%/.!+,*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BBorder NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,360,350,120,260,000,100
PN,35904
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F359A1777129865
OL,3,CRunning champion raises over #46,000
OL,4,Cfollowing his death
OL,6,F"It is made up of highly trained
OL,7,Fvolunteers who are available 24 hours
OL,8,Fa day, 365 days a year to respond to
OL,9,Femergencies in the mountains and
OL,10,Fremote areas of Scotland, and it
OL,11,Frelies on donations in order to carry
OL,12,Fout it's great work."
OL,14,FDavid Parrish was attempting to run
OL,15,Fthe fastest known time for the Cape
OL,16,FWrath Trail, unsupported, "through bog
OL,17,Fand bealach from Fort William to the
OL,18,FCape Wrath lighthouse".
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G4/7
OL,2,W/.!+.!/*%/.!+,*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
