FL,360,350,120,260,000,100
PN,35905
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F359A1777129865
OL,3,CRunning champion raises over #46,000
OL,4,Cfollowing his death
OL,6,FDonations now in his memory continue
OL,7,Fto rise and includes #1000 from fellow
OL,8,Frunners at Dumfries running club.
OL,10,FAmong the tributes pouring in on his
OL,11,Ffundraising page are comments such as:
OL,12,F"Truly up there with the kindest, most
OL,13,Fgenuine blokes I've ever met. Your joy
OL,14,Fand high spirits would lighten up any
OL,15,Froom. Truly blessed to have shared the
OL,16,Fstomping ground with you."
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G5/7
OL,2,W/.!+.!/*%/.!+,*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
