FL,360,350,120,260,000,100
PN,35906
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F359A1777129865
OL,3,CRunning champion raises over #46,000
OL,4,Cfollowing his death
OL,6,FOne fellow runner wrote: "A really
OL,7,Fgenuine, humble guy, hugely talented
OL,8,Frunner with scope to achieve so much
OL,9,Fmore and will be an inspiration to
OL,10,Fmany others."
OL,12,FAnother simply reads, "a huge loss to
OL,13,Fthe running community." While many
OL,14,Fshare the sentiment, "Thinking of your
OL,15,Ffiance, family and friends."
